JOB DESCRIPTION
Job Title： Package Processing Manager Position Type： full time Salary： $2500-$3100 /mo
Basic position overview：
The key function of this position is to receive, combine into a single package, if necessary and forward all incoming mail, performing warehouse duties such as unloading and handling.
Here are the fundamental position requirements (no prior experience is necessary).
Essential Tasks：
- Receive all packages from various services;
- Check quality of packages;
- Sort forward all incoming mail;
- Print shipment labels;
Requirements, knowledge and abilities：
- Willingness to work in a fast paced atmosphere;
- Basic computer experience;
- Ability to travel infrequently (optional);
- Candidate must be minimum 20 y.o.;
- Maintain awareness of sent packages and tasks assigned, and effectively communicate the status of these tasks to the supervisor.
- Ability to follow work instructions and safety methods;
We offers a competitive compensation and package for the effort including
- Career advancement, additional bonuses;
- participation in 401k and employee purchase program;
- Tuition Reimbursement, life insurance;
- Medical, dental benefits, full health coverage;
- Athletic club memberships.
